                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Advancement"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ". Money and power can be gained more easily within an organization. I plan to gain as much as possible. (Evil)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Structure"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ". Life goes much more smoothly when you follow the rules and work within a system. (Lawful)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "3"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Uncertainty"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ". The more chaos that swirls around me, the more opportunities I can find to profit. (Chaotic)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "4"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Justice"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ". I can't stand people being treated unjustly. I do whatever it takes to stop injustice and those who flout the law. (Lawful)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "5"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Pleasure"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ". What's the use of working hard and making money if you can't enjoy the finer things in life? (Any)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "6"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Power"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ". Money is fine, but real power means never having to say you're sorry. (Evil)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
